reviewText:
It's that time for the WWE Divas to pack up their swimsuits and head to Mexico for some fun in the sun. More beautiful than ever, the ladies show how talented they are in the ring and in front of the camera posing for the WWE Divas 2004 magazine.

Divas in the Ring - 10 Extra Matches
6 Magazine Photo Shoots
Interviews fromWWE Confidential with Torrie Wilson, Sable & Stacy Keibler
Exclusive Trish cam
7 Hidden extras
Plus more...
No Terri or Shaniqua. Terri was released from WWE and I dunno about Shaniqua.

I watched this DVD in Canada last month @ WWE Canada, and it rocked!! I don't know if all these features will be on the US version, but I can only hope!!!

The WWE Divas head down south of the border to mexico for the 2004 Divas Magazine Shoot. The divas particpated were Victoria, Ivory, Trish Stratus, Molly Holly, Gail Kim, Jazz, Jacqueline, Stacy Keibler, Lita, Miss Jackie, Torrie Wilson, Dawn Marie, Sable and Nidia. This DVD should be packed with extras for you which may contain Lita's return (Molly Holly & Gail Kim vs. Trish Stratus) Miss Jackie & Stacy Keibler uniting (Rico with Miss Jackie vs. Rob Conway with Renee Dupree) or Sables return (Torrie Wilson's Playboy Celebration). Also interviews with Torrie Wilson, Stacy Keibler and Sable from Confidential, Exclusive Trish Cam and Hidden Extras.
Amazing DVD so much of the great Divas from back when WWE television was interesting with a lot of extras and great matches I'll be sure to order another from amazon very pleased great DVD 5 Stars!!
This DVD is interesting but it could use a few more extras (more actual matches). As with all these DVD's it gives us a look at the ladies personalities.
Who cares about the photoshoots? i just wanted to see the wrestling matches but of course they are all 2 minutes. waste of time and money

When I first saw this I didn't think much of it, but now that it's 2012 and the divas division in WWE is in a downward spiral I took a look back at these dvds and thought, "Wow, the divas division was so awesome back then! What happened???"

This has got the same 1 hour special that they did every year (at that time) but with lots and lots of extras. Bunch of great matches, escpescially Victoria vs. Lita in the first ever (and only) WWE Divas Steel Cage Match. Plus lots of features from WWE Confidential (another great show that sadly got the ax).

this dvd was good for the whole thing about the divas and the shoot. but i didn't really like the match selection i would take out the halloween fun with torrie and Dawn marie because that was gay, also i would take out the burbon street bikkini match cuz that was stupid it just showed highlights, the last thing i would take out is the sable invtational because that was also gay. i would replace them with these SmackDown: Shaniqua vs Nidia & Torrie Wilson, Raw: Fatal Four Way to Determine #1 Contender for WWE WOmens Championship at Survivor Series, Gail vs Lita vs Victoria vs Trish, the last is SmackDown: Torrie Wilson vs Nidia qith SAble as the specail Referre

All of the WWE's sexiest females head to Mexico for the 2004 photo shoot. It's eye candy galore as Trish Stratus, Stacy Keibler, Torrie Wilson, Sable, Lita, Dawn Marie, Victoria, Ivory, Nidia, Miss Jackie, Molly, Gail Kim, Jacqueline, and Jazz pose for provactive photographs while commenting on the importance of this magazine on their careers. If you're expecting anything more than a bunch of gorgeous ladies posing in bikinis on the beach then save your money.

Wow. From what I'm reading of reviews about this item, you'd think they expect a company like the WWE to be making mass-circulation porn for the masses. I hardly think the WWE wants their female stars to be used in the same sentences as Aria Giovanni or Jenna Jameson (big-time porn stars, if you didn't know).
This DVD is designed to show off the beautiful bodies of these athletes, and if you want hot women, this ain't a bad place to start. Have you seen Stacy Kiebler!?! DAMN!!!
Lots of sultry poses, tight bods in bikinis, and sexy locations. This ain't about full sex or nudity, it's about teasing - cheap thrills, if you will. Don't take it as anything more than that, and you'll like this DVD.

If you watched wrestling you could see the change in the womens area happening over the 70's andbeyond.
The women in this video were an important part of that change. Most were georgous and weren't just fill in
performers. It was during that time that fitness was a booming industry and it was great to see in shape
beautiful women who could perform almost to the level that the men did. It even got better.
